data.description: Secluded and private this 20-acre ranch is nothing short of spectacular. 11.24 acres that has irrigation water rights.  Lush, irrigated fields, room for all your animals small and large. Huge metal barn. 3-bedroom 2 bath with heated tile floors in the bathroom. Enter into the living room with vaulted ceilings and a breathtaking Montana Rock fireplace. Beautiful granite counter tops, cherry wood cabinets, 3 bedrooms that are spacious, light and bright. Kitchen is warm and inviting with plenty of room for everyone to gather. Enjoy entertaining friends and family on the deck looking out at the pond or just enjoying everything this ranch has to offer. There is plenty of room for your friends and family to come and stay in the guest houses. Pristine trees, exceptional multi-use land and buildings. barn, hay storage, gardening. chicken coop, sauna, green house. Just minutes to downtown Bend, hiking, golfing, skiing & rafting.
